CHOLERA, IMPORTED - USA: REQUEST FOR INFO
*************************
A ProMED post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
Date: Fri 29 Oct 1999
From: Marianne Hopp <mhopp@students.wisc.edu>
Source: WHO Weekly Epidemiological Record

Notifications received from 22 to 28 October 1999
C ­ cases, D ­ deaths, ... ­ data not yet received,
i ­ imported, r ­ revised, s ­ suspect
DISEASES SUBJECT TO THE REGULATIONS
Cholera
Americas
Cases Deaths
United States of America 5-VIII [5 Aug 1999]
1i 0
[As usual, we would like to know the country of origin of the infection
& the strain of cholera involved -- and to remind the reporting country
that notifying at the end of October a case which occurred in August is
not fulfilling the obligation to report a suspected case of cholera to
WHO within 24 hours - Mod.JW]
..................................................jw
